text: Jinzaburō, Jinzaburo or Jinzaburou (written: 甚三郎 or 仁三郎) is a masculine Japanese given name. Notable people with the name include: *, Japanese general *, Japanese nuclear chemist and writer *Jinzaburo Yonezawa (born 1977), Japanese mixed martial artist Category:Japanese masculine given names
